One of my most common use-cases for Confluence-JIRA integration is to annotate a spec with related issues (example: https://studio.atlassian.com/wiki/display/STRM/Streams+4+UI+Changes).

To make this work well, I need a compact representation of the issues. Often, one that doesn't include the summary. I'd like the ability to configure the fields shown. A "compact" view that shows {{priority_icon issue_key - status_text}}, but not issue type icon, summary, or status icon, would be of huge use to me.

